Muchidzo che[[Kupimanzvimbo]] ''(Geometry)'', [[chidzudzani]] zvinoreva kuti zvivakwa zviviri zvine [[chiumbwa]] ''(shape)'' chakafanana uye [[hukuru]] (size) hwakaenzana. Izvi zvoreva kuti chiumbwa chokutanga chinokwanisa kushandurwa mamiriro kusvikira chati gedye-gedye kupindirana nechiumbwa chepiri; zvimwechitezvo tichitanga kushanda nechiumbwa chepiri. KuEnglish izwi rokuti [[chidzudzani]] rinoturikirwa richinzi ''congruency''.

==Kupiwa kwezita==

Zita rokuti [[chidzudzani]] riri kutoredzera pamutauro wemazuvano ''(slang)'' panonzi nevatyairi vemabhazi, ''nhasi radzudza vachireva kuti bhazi razara''. Zviumbwa zvine [[chidzudzani]] zvinozadzana mupimo wemativi nemakonya. Chimwe chinoonekwa pazviumbwa zvine chidzudzani ndechekuti kuringana kwemativi nemakonya ezviumbwa zviri kufananidzwa.
